          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-1" n="1">With half an Eye</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-2" n="2">Your Riddle I spy</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-3" n="3">I observe your Wicket</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-4" n="4">Hem'd in by a Thicket</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-5" n="5">And what ever passes</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-6" n="6">Is strained thro' Glasses</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-7" n="7">You're reported to dwell</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-8" n="8">Like a Monck in a Cell</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-9" n="9">You say it is quiet</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-10" n="10">I flatly deny it</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-11" n="11">It wanders about</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-12" n="12">Without stirring out</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-13" n="13">No passion so weak</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-14" n="14">But gives it a Tweak</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-15" n="15">Love Joy and Devotion</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-16" n="16">Set it always on Motion</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-17" n="17">And as for the Tragick</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-18" n="18">Effects of its Magick</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-19" n="19">When you say it can kill</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-20" n="20">Or revive when it will</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-21" n="21">The Slain are all Sound</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-22" n="22">And revive above Ground</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-23" n="23">After all you have writ</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-24" n="24">It cannot be wit</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-25" n="25">W.<hi rend="superscript">ch</hi>──  clearly does follow</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-26" n="26">Since it flies f<hi rend="superscript">m</hi>- Apollo</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-27" n="27">Its cowardice such</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-28" n="28">That it cries at a touch</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-29" n="29">Its a perfect milk sop</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-30" n="30">Grows drunk w<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>──  a drop</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-31" n="31">Another great fault</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-32" n="32">It cannot bear Salt</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-33" n="33">And a hair can disarm</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938B020B-line-34" n="34">It of every Charm</l>
          </lg>
